									</ul>
								</p>
								<h4>GitHub Game Off 2018</h4>

								<p>
									The <a href="https://itch.io/jam/game-off-2018">Game Off</a> is GitHub's annual game jam, where participants spend the month of November creating games based on a theme.
								</p>
								<p>
									<ul class="unordered">
										<li><strong>Theme:</strong> Hybrid</li>
										<li><strong>Dates:</strong> November 1st to December 1st, 2018</li>
										<li><strong>Number of submissions:</strong> 323</li>
									</ul>
								</p>
								<p>
									<h4>Results for <a href="https://itch.io/jam/game-off-2018/rate/338002">Spork</a></h4>
									<ul>
										<li>Overall: 134th </li>
										<li>Gameplay: 168th </li>
										<li>Innovation: 32nd</li>
										<li>Theme Interpretation: 34th </li>
